WESTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
STRAITS OF FLORIDA.
BAHAMAS TO FLORIDA.
25 FOOT VESSEL, DARK BLUE AND WHITE HULL,
FOUR PERSONS ON BOARD, OVERDUE GUN CAY
(25-34-13N 079-17-51W) TO MIAMI (25-47-16N 080-13-27W).
VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT,
ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO U.S. COAST GUARD RCC MIAMI,
PHONE: 305 415 6800, E-MAIL: RCCMIAMI@USCG.MIL.
